{"tid":1634870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實可唔可以唔好再叫人企鬆啲？","createTime":"2019-10-07T10:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T10:33:13.000Z","uid":264368,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cd135d5243bb0742af6d50f9691db1e713eb8877","tid":1634870,"uid":264368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:31:18.000Z","msg":"一個都不少？<br />\n如果希望大眾有反抗覺悟，<span style=\"color: orange;\">點解要培養走佬既意識？</span><br />\n包括行動既考慮focus撤退、分過多區、叫人企鬆啲etc.<br />\n<br />\n點解要開催淚彈？<br />\n有冇見過黑警衝向<span style=\"color: orange;\">一大堆面向住佢地</span>既人？<br />\n有冇見過黑警可以喺<span style=\"color: orange;\">一大堆唔係走緊佬</span>既人入面拉到人出黎？<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">就係要示威者分散</span>，先能夠進行追捕<br />\n如果冇分散，佢地又點能夠進行追捕？<br />\n<br />\n我地玩唔到亦唔可以玩過份武力，所以<span style=\"color: orange;\">只可以玩數量</span><br />\n<br />\n各式各樣減少每一群示威者人數既風向，又或者企鬆啲之類，根本就係培養緊走佬既意識，<span style=\"color: orange;\">要示威者自動分散</span>，如果我係黑警，一定笑爆咀，唔洗開槍你地都<span style=\"color: orange;\">自己分散哂比人捉</span>。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，無論hitandrun定陣地戰，示威者都<span style=\"color: red;\">唔應該分散至少於100人</span>，視乎對面有幾多隻。<br />\n唔需要夠膽反擊，只需要夠多人stick together。<br />\n遇到催淚彈又好，防暴推進又好，嘗試<span style=\"color: red;\">企埋啲</span>，至少100人一堆<span style=\"color: red;\">面向</span>防暴慢慢退，<span style=\"color: red;\">齊上齊落</span>。<br />\n<br />\n當然，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔夠人既情況下</span>一定要以最快速度離開。<br />\n<br />\n另外，亦希望減少培養雞飛狗走心態，應多鼓勵同伴之間既照應、協助、合作等等。<br />\n<br />\n最後，懇求場上既人<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好亂嗌有狗</span>，咁樣會製造不必要既恐慌，嚴重影響形勢，真正威脅在場人士既安全。<br />\n<br />\n得啦，實有人話分化撚，有更好既見解或者意見可以討論一下，我只係唔希望再有依啲片段，香港人需要再進步得快啲，多謝各位。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B3Tv6XrFNTX/?igshid=rfmiqkqq37xo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB3Tv6XrFNTX%2F%3Figshid%3Drfmiqkqq37xo&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn5MONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=f3d1e2b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB3Tv6XrFNTX%2F%3Figshid%3Drfmiqkqq37xo&h=29098b50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B3Tv6XrFNTX/?igshid=rfmiqkqq37xo</a>"},{"pid":"be2edfb9fa426488f9b375f134cf00859d19ff28","tid":1634870,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:31:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOnWv33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOnWv33.jpg&h=e36634e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae5eee6d99819cae82977b62554e66d52c245ef0","tid":1634870,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:33:13.000Z","msg":"【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家繼續做落去！（分析長文）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文見此：<br />\n<br />\n【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家一定要繼續做落去！（分析長文）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a>"}]}